Coding Challenge Set: Strings & Tuples   
 
 Challenge 1: Student Name Formatting 
A student database stores names in inconsistent formats. 
 Task 
Convert all names to proper case (First letter capital). 
   Input 
students = ("sunitha", "RAVI", "aNu") 
 
 Challenge 2: Count Total Subjects 
Each student has subjects stored in a tuple. 
   Input 
subjects = ("Math", "Science", "English", "Math", "Science") 
 Task 
Find: 
• Total subjects  
• Unique subjects  
 
Challenge 3: Remove Extra Spaces from Feedback 
Student feedback contains unwanted spaces. 
   Input 
feedback = ("  good course  ", " excellent ", "average  ") 
 Task 
Clean all feedback strings 
 
 Challenge 4: Combine Student Name & Course 
You have separate tuples for names and courses. 
   Input 
names = ("Anu", "Ravi", "John") 
courses = ("Python", "SQL", "Power BI") 
 Task 
Create a tuple: 
('Anu-Python', 'Ravi-SQL', 'John-Power BI') 
 
 Challenge 5: Extract Email Domains 
Student emails are stored in tuple. 
   Input 
emails = ("anu@gmail.com", "ravi@yahoo.com", "john@edu.com") 
 Task 
Extract domains 
